commit.title: Delimiters: give printing priority to the delimiters used last for parsing.
commit.message:
Delimiters: give printing priority to the delimiters used last for parsing.

Examples:

Check (true || true)%bool.
(* (true || true)%bool *)

Check (true || true)%B.
(* (true || true)%B *)
